Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_rst_cntl#

Notes: GEN1_Only mode is enabled for PEM0 when QLM1_SPD[0] is set or when sclk < 550Mhz. GEN1_Only mode is enabled for PEM1 when QLM1_SPD[1] is set or when sclk < 550Mhz.
